window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p><b>The gang’s all here!</b></p> <p>After successfully stopping the cult of the Necrolord from discovering the location of the <i>Book of Vile Dankness</i>, the party is en route to acquire the artifact and keep it out of the Necrolord’s hands!</p> <p>This time, they must deal with ghouls, golems, and a very musically inspired tarasque. Meanwhile, another group of adventurers is on a quest to recover the book and will do everything necessary to get the book for themselves.</p> <p>Discover how Samo, Wyatt, Bourbon, Falcon, and Melf contend with this latest challenge!</p>"; 
